1
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,680
Father.

2
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,319
This is how things stand.

3
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,680
Why not give Ning Ziming a warning?

4
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,719
Tell him to stop shielding that bastard.

5
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:36,719
So you're saying

6
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:39,120
that Ning Ziming

7
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:41,640
fears His Majesty.

8
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,000
Grandfather.

9
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:48,000
Has he truly caught His Majesty's eye?

10
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,319
What has he done to deserve that?

11
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,359
Exactly, Grandfather.

12
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,120
That bastard Ning Chen,

13
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,840
we used to bully him plenty.

14
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,640
But now he's joined the Imperial Inspectorate.

15
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,319
Could it be

16
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,920
he's actually turning his fortunes around?

17
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,879
What if he comes back for revenge?

18
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,200
What are we going to do?

19
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,959
Xing'er has a point.

20
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,560
With his Silver Guard status in the Inspectorate,

21
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,759
and Ning Ziming shielding him,

22
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:12,120
he might claim a share of the Ning estate.

23
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:12,840
Exactly, Grandfather.

24
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,000
Grandfather, we can't let this happen!

25
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:14,919
What do we do about this?

26
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,120
What's the panic?

27
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,400
I am, after all, head of all the officials.

28
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,759
He's just a mere Silver Guard.

29
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,800
What trouble could he possibly stir up?

30
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:26,879
Guards.

31
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:30,240
Your orders, Lord Chancellor?

32
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,280
Go to the Imperial Inspectorate.

33
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,439
Have them keep a close watch on Ning Chen.

34
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,000
Find an opportunity

35
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:39,759
to eliminate him with full justification.

36
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,639
We must not give His Majesty

37
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,960
any reason to find fault.

38
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,680
Yes, my lord.

39
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,240
Big brother.

40
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,080
The Imperial Inspectorate is restricted ground.

41
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,800
No outsiders allowed.

42
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,159
Outsiders?

43
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:19,159
I'm a big shot reporting in by imperial decree.

44
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,840
You?

45
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:23,680
What?

46
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:24,759
You...

47
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:25,960
Golden Guard Pan has arrived!

48
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,199
Greetings, Golden Guard Pan.

49
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,879
So you're Ning Chen.

50
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,639
That would be me.

51
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:40,800
Follow me.

52
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:47,439
Park the carriage properly.

53
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:48,840
Ask your boss for the tip.

54
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:53,719
The Inspectorate has one Purple Guard

55
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,719
who oversees everything.

56
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:57,000
Eight Golden Guards head eight departments,

57
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:58,599
each in charge of

58
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,039
investigation and arrests,

59
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,719
weapons and equipment research,

60
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:05,439
medical care, logistics, and so on.

61
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,879
The eight departments have different roles,

62
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,000
each handling its own...

63
00:04:11,599 --> 00:04:12,840
It only fires one bolt at a time?

64
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,240
That's so outdated.

65
00:04:14,719 --> 00:04:17,120
I'll upgrade it to a Zhuge repeater later.

66
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,279
I'm talking to you.

67
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:24,879
I heard you.

68
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,639
From now on, you're with me,

69
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,480
handling investigation and arrests.

70
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,040
Hey, boss.

71
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,560
Call me Golden Guard Pan.

72
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,800
Greetings, Golden Guard Pan.

73
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,839
Get him a set of Silver Guard robes.

74
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:39,839
Change quickly.

75
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,639
Once you're changed,

76
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:42,319
meet me at the gate. I'll introduce you.

77
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:43,879
Got it.

78
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,439
That look on your face,

79
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:53,120
you don't think much of me?

80
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,519
How much do you weigh, buddy?

81
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,319
Two hundred.

82
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:39,199
Over two hundred. You're pretty strong.

83
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,560
Does your hand hurt?

84
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,079
Next time I'll get you a sandbag.

85
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,800
Impressive moves.

86
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,240
Stand up.

87
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:27,920
Put your hat on.

88
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:33,560
Brothers,

89
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:36,199
let me introduce a new recruit.

90
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:39,560
Go on, introduce yourself.

91
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,839
Greetings, brothers.

92
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,040
My name is Ning Chen.

93
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,160
I look forward to working with you.

94
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,160
Hold on.

95
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,360
The Inspectorate recruits at the start of the year, no?

96
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,560
Don't tell me

97
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,800
he's another one who pulled strings to get in.

98
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,000
Um, Ning...

99
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,439
Handsome Ning here

100
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,680
This Ning

101
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:06,319
is a Silver Guard personally appointed by His Majesty.

102
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:07,199
And what's more,

103
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,439
he's Minister Ning's son from House Ning.

104
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,000
Chief, I have to say,

105
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,279
a pampered young lord coming to our Inspectorate

106
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,560
is utterly useless.

107
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:19,040
He'll only mess things up for us.

108
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,439
Old Gao, that's enough out of you.

109
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,680
A pampered lord like him

110
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,399
could never endure the hardships here.

111
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:25,600
Besides, His Majesty

112
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,040
would never allow a minister's son

113
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:28,279
to stay long with us.

114
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,079
Just bear with it.

115
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,199
He'll be gone soon enough.

116
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,199
No, you've misunder--

117
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:31,800
Enough.

118
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,560
Bring out today's case files.

119
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,120
Right away.

120
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,079
Don't interrupt when grown-ups are talking, kid.

121
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:38,879
Step aside.

122
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:41,879
Chief.

123
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:44,519
The coroner has examined Squire Zhang's body.

124
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,199
Just as we suspected,

125
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,079
the killer is about five feet seven.

126
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,160
And the murder weapon

127
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,439
matches our deduction as well.

128
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,360
It was a dagger.

129
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,000
What's more, the wound

130
00:07:53,199 --> 00:07:54,000
runs from below upward,

131
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:54,720
which means...

132
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,560
That tells us this killer

133
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,800
must be shorter than Squire Zhang.

134
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:07,199
And Squire Zhang took seven stab wounds,

135
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,199
but the wounds...

136
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:09,879
Got something to say?

137
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,439
Go on.

138
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,480
The wounds are all very shallow.

139
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,839
Which means this killer

140
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,920
can't have been very strong.

141
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:21,240
According to his concubine and his son,

142
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:21,759
this killer

143
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,120
leapt onto the rooftop with ease.

144
00:08:23,759 --> 00:08:24,240
This killer...

145
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,920
These people rely too much on assumptions

146
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:28,240
but the corpse is the most honest witness.

147
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,160
A master needing seven stabs to kill?

148
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,600
Use your head.

149
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,480
Hold on, here's what we figured.

150
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,600
Maybe it was the killer's first time.

151
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,879
Or maybe it was accidental.

152
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,159
For instance,

153
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,519
he was stealing something

154
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,799
and got caught by accident,

155
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,679
so he resorted to murder.

156
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,120
Did you check the roof?

157
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,799
We did. The tiles are intact.

158
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:45,960
Not a single trace.

159
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,720
Boss, could it be the rain a few days ago

160
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,120
washed all the evidence away?

161
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:52,960
I have a question.

162
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,240
How old is the Squire Zhang you mentioned?

163
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:57,600
Want to know?

164
00:08:58,879 --> 00:08:59,879
What do you think that thing's for?

165
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,000
Come look for yourself.

166
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,600
Boss, I think there's

167
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,320
another possibility here.

168
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,399
Put your hat on properly.

169
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,759
Squire Zhang took seven stab wounds,

170
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,720
and the wounds are all very shallow.

171
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,399
Which means this killer

172
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,399
can't have been very strong.

173
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,919
According to his concubine and his son,

174
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,759
this killer leapt onto the roof with ease.

175
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:23,840
Did you check the roof?

176
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,600
Tiles intact. Not a single trace.

177
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,279
The wounds vary in depth.

178
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,240
It's more like the victim struggled violently,

179
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,039
and the killer couldn't overpower him,

180
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,159
which left him exhausted.

181
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,559
A master who can scale walls

182
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:35,399
needing seven stabs to kill an old man?

183
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,159
Unless...

184
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,799
this master doesn't exist at all,

185
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,600
but two people, neither being very strong,

186
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,919
killing him together.

187
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,480
What does a rich boy know?

188
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,879
Actually, I know a thing or two.

189
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:47,120
I wandered the streets since childhood,

190
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,559
only brought back to the Ning estate at twelve.

191
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:52,240
So when it comes to the harshness of life,

192
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,120
you two haven't seen more than I have.

193
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:57,559
Young Master Ning,

194
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,480
allow me to enlighten you.

195
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,480
To get by in our line of work,

196
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,960
you need real skill.

197
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:05,559
Playing the pity card

198
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,759
won't help.

199
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:10,320
Is it possible

200
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,120
that this testimony isn't truthful?

201
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,440
The killer you speak of

202
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,679
simply doesn't exist at all.

203
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,080
Could it be...

204
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:29,480
Squire Zhang's son and concubine lied?

205
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,840
The lad shows promise.

206
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:33,879
See?

207
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,639
Don't embarrass yourself, Young Master Ning.

208
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,120
Zhang Mingjie is Squire Zhang's only son.

209
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:41,720
Once Squire Zhang dies,

210
00:10:41,879 --> 00:10:43,080
the entire estate goes to him.

211
00:10:43,279 --> 00:10:45,480
Why would he kill for what's already his?

212
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:48,240
But Squire Zhang was advanced in years,

213
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,799
while his concubine is only thirty,

214
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,799
in the prime of her hungry years.

215
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,559
And his son?

216
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,679
Twenty-five.

217
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,960
Just the age that can't resist temptation.

218
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,759
This...

219
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,679
Come on, get up.

220
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,639
Who do you think you are, sitting there?

221
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:07,480
Listen here.

222
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:09,799
As the only son of the Zhang family,

223
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,879
what woman could he not have?

224
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,840
Why fall for his stepmother?

225
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,399
Truly a pampered young master.

226
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,519
Mind full of filth and lust.

227
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,840
Hey, come on now.

228
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,159
Sleeping with one's stepmother

229
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,559
defies all morals and propriety.

230
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,000
Zhang Mingjie is at least a scholar,

231
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,000
a man of reason.

232
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,159
How could he stoop to such depravity?

233
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:25,840
Don't believe me?

234
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:28,000
Investigate.

235
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,039
See?

236
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:30,639
Quiet.

237
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:33,879
What he said

238
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,039
does have some merit.

239
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,320
Since we have no other leads,

240
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,480
let's bring them in for questioning.

241
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,840
You two, go.

242
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,159
Look at you...

243
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,240
Go.

244
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:48,639
Go, go, go.

245
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:02,600
Zhang Mingjie, confess at once!

246
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,679
My lord, it wasn't me!

247
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:05,759
My lord!

248
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:08,799
My lord!

249
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:11,399
I truly know nothing!

250
00:12:14,639 --> 00:12:15,320
My lord!

251
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:20,960
Boss.

252
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,320
I told you this young master is useless.

253
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,360
He just loves spouting nonsense.

254
00:12:23,879 --> 00:12:24,960
Now he's playing with toy blocks.

255
00:12:25,399 --> 00:12:25,879
Well?

256
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:26,919
Boss,

257
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:28,799
we have no evidence, only guesses.

258
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,720
Those two were utterly heartbroken.

259
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:32,440
It wasn't right to press them further.

260
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,320
These two are the killers.

261
00:13:00,399 --> 00:13:01,759
"These two are the killers," he says.

262
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:02,840
Listen, young master.

263
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:04,600
This is a matter of life and death.

264
00:13:04,759 --> 00:13:06,840
Not an idle game of falcons and crickets.

265
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:10,519
Sir.

266
00:13:12,399 --> 00:13:13,559
Take a look at these two confessions.

267
00:13:14,159 --> 00:13:15,799
The answer lies within them.

268
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,759
When people are frightened,

269
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,360
or in extreme grief,

270
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,200
their speech usually becomes incoherent.

271
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:26,960
In other words, as we often say,

272
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,639
their words don't quite add up.

273
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,519
But these two confessions

274
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,200
are perfectly coherent.

275
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:34,600
As if cast from the same mold.

276
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:38,759
Sir,

277
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:39,799
I have a suggestion.

278
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:42,039
You should look into

279
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:44,600
Squire Zhang's concubine's personal maid.

280
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,159
An affair like this

281
00:13:46,279 --> 00:13:47,200
can be hidden from others,

282
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,919
but never from a personal maid.

283
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:50,360
During such trysts,

284
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,519
someone has to keep watch.

285
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,360
And that person

286
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:55,759
is usually the one she trusts most.

287
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,600
So young,

288
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,240
yet so composed,

289
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,440
and so sharp-minded.

290
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,120
What a pity.

291
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,399
You two,

292
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,200
go bring her in.

293
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:10,240
Wait, boss...

294
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:10,919
Go on, hurry.

295
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,080
Him, him, me...

296
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:12,600
Him, me...

297
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,080
Come on, come on, let's go together.

298
00:14:14,799 --> 00:14:15,919
Back and forth with you, always so chatty.

299
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:16,440
We're off.

300
00:14:18,799 --> 00:14:20,200
Sir, what about me?

301
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:22,759
You?

302
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,519
You're off duty.

303
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:28,399
I'm off duty just like that?

304
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,080
But I haven't done anything yet.

305
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:31,279
They can handle it.

306
00:14:33,879 --> 00:14:35,879
I know you're young and eager,

307
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:36,879
hungry to earn merit.

308
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:37,679
But you see,

309
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,720
your status is special, after all.

310
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:41,200
I can't have you taking on

311
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,919
the kind of jobs that risk your neck.

312
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,279
If anything happened to you,

313
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:47,559
the Inspectorate couldn't face House Ning.

314
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,399
So that's the real reason.

315
00:14:51,279 --> 00:14:52,240
Others fight tooth and nail,

316
00:14:52,399 --> 00:14:53,519
yet still have to share credit with me.

317
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:55,120
No wonder they resent me.

318
00:14:55,879 --> 00:14:56,519
Golden Guard Pan.

319
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:59,039
I am simply Ning Chen.

320
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,360
I have nothing to do with House Ning.

321
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:04,039
Do as you please.

